# Style Consistency First

Before coding, inspect similar files in this repository and mirror their style.

- Prefer established naming, import order, and file structure over personal preference.
- Match existing patterns in the same app/package before introducing new abstractions.
- Favor libraries and utilities already used in this repo.
- If conventions look inconsistent, follow the most recent local pattern in the touched area.
- Do not perform broad style refactors unless explicitly requested.
